data.description: Stunning 3 bed/2 bath ranch home built by Bridwell Homes, conveniently located in Old Town Rock Hill within walking distance to Downtown Rock Hill. High-end finishes and features throughout, fun touches of color and style, you'll love this home for all it offers. Modern open floor plan with kitchen island, title backsplash, built in 2020 on a corner lot with large yard and insulated tree house ideal for a man-cave or she-shed. Schedule your showings today!
